QuestData.Title: At Your Command
QuestData.Description: I'm glad you're here!$B$BFort Wrynn is nearly complete. We only need to fill this last plot.$B$BBaros provided us with blueprints for two different structures that would fit this space - an Artillery Tower or an Arcane Sanctum.$B$BIt's your call, commander. The plans are on the drafting table for your perusal.
QuestData.LogDescription: Choose which outpost structure to construct.
